    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept good-condition car that presents nicely and appears complete, usable, and ready to enjoy as a solid driver. Paint, trim, and interior show normal age and use, but overall it looks cared for and should make a satisfying car for someone who wants a presentable, honest example rather than a fully restored showpiece. Expect a car that is tidy and appealing, with some wear consistent with use, but nothing about it suggests neglect.",
